<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8" />
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
<title>Asteroid8 — Live Music, Reimagined</title>
<meta name="description" content="Asteroid8 is where music goes live. Join live concerts, parties, and orbit jams. Stream, chart, and connect with artists in real time." />
<link rel="icon" href="astei.png" />
<meta property="og:title" content="Asteroid8 — Live Music, Reimagined" />
<meta property="og:description" content="Live concerts, parties, and orbit jams. Music that happens in real time." />
<meta property="og:image" content="astei.png" />
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com" />
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin />
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@300;400;500;600;700;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet" />
<style>
  :root{
    --coral:#FF7F50;
    --coral-soft:#ff9d78;
    --bg:#08090c;
    --bg-2:#0e1016;
    --panel:#13151d;
    --line:rgba(255,255,255,.07);
    --txt:#f4f5f7;
    --muted:#9aa0ad;
  }
  *{margin:0;padding:0;box-sizing:border-box}
  html{scroll-behavior:smooth}
  body{
    font-family:'Inter',-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,sans-serif;
    background:var(--bg);
    color:var(--txt);
    line-height:1.6;
    overflow-x:hidden;
    -webkit-font-smoothing:antialiased;
  }
  a{color:inherit;text-decoration:none}
  .wrap{max-width:1140px;margin:0 auto;padding:0 24px}

  /* glow backdrop */
  .glow{position:fixed;inset:0;z-index:-1;pointer-events:none}
  .glow::before,.glow::after{content:"";position:absolute;border-radius:50%;filter:blur(120px);opacity:.32}
  .glow::before{width:520px;height:520px;background:var(--coral);top:-160px;right:-120px}
  .glow::after{width:460px;height:460px;background:#5b6cff;bottom:-180px;left:-140px;opacity:.18}

  /* nav */
  nav{position:sticky;top:0;z-index:50;backdrop-filter:blur(14px);background:rgba(8,9,12,.6);border-bottom:1px solid var(--line)}
  nav .wrap{display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;height:68px}
  .brand{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:12px;font-weight:700;font-size:18px;letter-spacing:.3px}
  .brand img{width:32px;height:32px;border-radius:8px;object-fit:cover}
  .nav-links{display:flex;gap:34px;font-size:14px;color:var(--muted)}
  .nav-links a:hover{color:var(--txt)}
  .btn{display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;padding:11px 22px;border-radius:100px;font-weight:600;font-size:14px;transition:.25s;border:1px solid transparent;cursor:pointer}
  .btn-primary{background:var(--coral);color:#1a0c05;box-shadow:0 8px 30px rgba(255,127,80,.35)}
  .btn-primary:hover{background:var(--coral-soft);transform:translateY(-2px);box-shadow:0 12px 38px rgba(255,127,80,.45)}
  .btn-ghost{border-color:var(--line);color:var(--txt)}
  .btn-ghost:hover{border-color:var(--coral);color:var(--coral)}
  @media(max-width:760px){.nav-links{display:none}}

  /* hero */
  header{padding:120px 0 100px;text-align:center;position:relative}
  .pill{display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;padding:7px 16px;border:1px solid var(--line);border-radius:100px;font-size:13px;color:var(--muted);margin-bottom:30px;background:rgba(255,255,255,.02)}
  .pill .dot{width:7px;height:7px;border-radius:50%;background:var(--coral);box-shadow:0 0 10px var(--coral);animation:pulse 1.8s infinite}
  @keyframes pulse{0%,100%{opacity:1}50%{opacity:.35}}
  h1{font-size:clamp(42px,7vw,80px);font-weight:800;line-height:1.04;letter-spacing:-2px;margin-bottom:24px}
  h1 .accent{background:linear-gradient(120deg,var(--coral),#ffd0bb);-webkit-background-clip:text;background-clip:text;color:transparent}
  header p.sub{font-size:clamp(17px,2.2vw,21px);color:var(--muted);max-width:620px;margin:0 auto 40px}
  .cta-row{display:flex;gap:14px;justify-content:center;flex-wrap:wrap}
  .btn-lg{padding:15px 30px;font-size:15px}

  /* stats */
  .stats{display:flex;gap:60px;justify-content:center;margin-top:70px;flex-wrap:wrap}
  .stat .n{font-size:34px;font-weight:800;color:var(--txt)}
  .stat .l{font-size:13px;color:var(--muted);text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:1.5px}

  /* sections */
  section{padding:90px 0}
  .eyebrow{color:var(--coral);font-size:13px;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:2px;text-transform:uppercase;margin-bottom:14px;text-align:center}
  h2{font-size:clamp(30px,4.5vw,46px);font-weight:800;letter-spacing:-1px;text-align:center;margin-bottom:14px}
  .section-sub{color:var(--muted);text-align:center;max-width:560px;margin:0 auto 56px;font-size:16px}

  .grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr);gap:20px}
  @media(max-width:880px){.grid{grid-template-columns:1fr}}
  .card{background:var(--panel);border:1px solid var(--line);border-radius:18px;padding:32px;transition:.3s}
  .card:hover{transform:translateY(-5px);border-color:rgba(255,127,80,.4);background:#161922}
  .card .ico{width:48px;height:48px;border-radius:12px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;font-size:24px;margin-bottom:18px;background:rgba(255,127,80,.12)}
  .card h3{font-size:19px;font-weight:700;margin-bottom:8px}
  .card p{color:var(--muted);font-size:15px}

  /* big feature band */
  .band{background:linear-gradient(180deg,var(--bg-2),var(--bg));border-top:1px solid var(--line);border-bottom:1px solid var(--line)}
  .band-inner{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:60px;align-items:center}
  @media(max-width:880px){.band-inner{grid-template-columns:1fr;gap:36px}}
  .band h2{text-align:left}
  .band ul{list-style:none;margin-top:24px;display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:16px}
  .band li{display:flex;gap:14px;align-items:flex-start;color:var(--muted)}
  .band li b{color:var(--txt);font-weight:600}
  .check{flex-shrink:0;width:24px;height:24px;border-radius:50%;background:rgba(255,127,80,.15);color:var(--coral);display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;font-size:13px;font-weight:700}
  .band-visual{aspect-ratio:1;border-radius:24px;background:radial-gradient(circle at 30% 20%,rgba(255,127,80,.4),transparent 60%),radial-gradient(circle at 80% 90%,rgba(91,108,255,.35),transparent 55%),var(--panel);border:1px solid var(--line);display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;position:relative;overflow:hidden}
  .band-visual img{width:42%;opacity:.92;filter:drop-shadow(0 20px 50px rgba(0,0,0,.5))}

  /* CTA */
  .final{text-align:center}
  .final .box{background:linear-gradient(135deg,rgba(255,127,80,.14),rgba(91,108,255,.1));border:1px solid var(--line);border-radius:28px;padding:70px 40px}
  .final h2{margin-bottom:16px}
  .final p{color:var(--muted);margin-bottom:32px;font-size:17px}

  /* footer */
  footer{border-top:1px solid var(--line);padding:48px 0;color:var(--muted);font-size:14px}
  footer .wrap{display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:center;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:18px}
  footer .f-links{display:flex;gap:26px}
  footer a:hover{color:var(--txt)}
</style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="glow"></div>

<nav>
  <div class="wrap">
    <a class="brand" href="/"><img src="astei.png" alt="Asteroid8" />Asteroid8</a>
    <div class="nav-links">
      <a href="#features">Features</a>
      <a href="#live">Live</a>
      <a href="charts.html">Charts</a>
      <a href="artist.html">For Artists</a>
    </div>
    <a class="btn btn-primary" href="index.html">Open App</a>
  </div>
</nav>

<header>
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="pill"><span class="dot"></span> Live now · concerts, parties &amp; orbit jams</div>
    <h1>Music that happens<br /><span class="accent">in real time.</span></h1>
    <p class="sub">Asteroid8 is the live stage for the internet. Drop into concerts, host parties, climb the charts, and jam with artists as it all unfolds — no replays, just now.</p>
    <div class="cta-row">
      <a class="btn btn-primary btn-lg" href="index.html">Launch Asteroid8 →</a>
      <a class="btn btn-ghost btn-lg" href="#features">Explore features</a>
    </div>
    <div class="stats">
      <div class="stat"><div class="n">24/7</div><div class="l">Live Stages</div></div>
      <div class="stat"><div class="n">∞</div><div class="l">Orbit Jams</div></div>
      <div class="stat"><div class="n">Real-time</div><div class="l">Charts</div></div>
    </div>
  </div>
</header>

<section id="features">
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="eyebrow">Why Asteroid8</div>
    <h2>One platform. Every way to go live.</h2>
    <p class="section-sub">Built for artists and fans who want music to feel alive — interactive, social, and happening right now.</p>
    <div class="grid">
      <div class="card">
        <div class="ico">🎤</div>
        <h3>Live Concerts</h3>
        <p>Step into front-row streams from artists around the world. Real performances, real crowds, zero buffering between you and the stage.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <div class="ico">🎉</div>
        <h3>Parties</h3>
        <p>Spin up a room, invite your people, and let the queue run. Shared listening that actually feels like being there together.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <div class="ico">🪐</div>
        <h3>Orbit Jams</h3>
        <p>Collaborative sessions where fans and creators build the set together — songs added, voted, and played in the moment.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <div class="ico">📈</div>
        <h3>Live Charts</h3>
        <p>Watch tracks rise as they're played. The charts move with the crowd, not a weekly report.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <div class="ico">💬</div>
        <h3>Live Chat</h3>
        <p>React, request, and connect in real time. Every stage comes with a room buzzing alongside it.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <div class="ico">⭐</div>
        <h3>Premium</h3>
        <p>Unlock higher fidelity, exclusive rooms, and creator perks that take your experience past the orbit.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<div class="band" id="live">
  <div class="wrap" style="padding-top:90px;padding-bottom:90px">
    <div class="band-inner">
      <div>
        <div class="eyebrow" style="text-align:left">For Artists</div>
        <h2>Your stage. Your crowd. Your charts.</h2>
        <p style="color:var(--muted);font-size:16px;margin-top:8px">Asteroid8 hands the controls to creators. Go live in seconds, grow a real-time audience, and turn plays into momentum.</p>
        <ul>
          <li><span class="check">✓</span><span><b>Instant broadcasting</b> — open the artist dashboard and you're live, no studio required.</span></li>
          <li><span class="check">✓</span><span><b>Real-time analytics</b> — see who's in the room and how your tracks are climbing.</span></li>
          <li><span class="check">✓</span><span><b>Direct fan connection</b> — chat, jams, and parties keep your audience close.</span></li>
          <li><span class="check">✓</span><span><b>Monetize your sound</b> — premium rooms and referrals built right in.</span></li>
        </ul>
        <div class="cta-row" style="justify-content:flex-start;margin-top:34px">
          <a class="btn btn-primary" href="artist.html">Become an Artist</a>
          <a class="btn btn-ghost" href="ArtistDashboard.html">View Dashboard</a>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="band-visual">
        <img src="astei.png" alt="Asteroid8" />
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<section class="final">
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="box">
      <h2>The stage is live. Step in.</h2>
      <p>Join Asteroid8 and experience music the way it was meant to be — in the moment.</p>
      <div class="cta-row">
        <a class="btn btn-primary btn-lg" href="index.html">Open Asteroid8 →</a>
        <a class="btn btn-ghost btn-lg" href="join.html">Create account</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<footer>
  <div class="wrap">
    <a class="brand" href="/"><img src="astei.png" alt="Asteroid8" style="width:26px;height:26px" />Asteroid8</a>
    <div class="f-links">
      <a href="features.html">Features</a>
      <a href="support.html">Support</a>
      <a href="policy.html">Privacy</a>
      <a href="Asteroid Terms.html">Terms</a>
    </div>
    <div>© 2025 Asteroid8. All rights reserved.</div>
  </div>
</footer>
</body>
</html>
